@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8082
@token = replace-with-login-access-token
@productId = 1
@orderId = 1

## 一、项目启动前检查
### 0. 服务健康测试
GET {{baseUrl}}/ping

## 二、商品模块正常流程
### 1. 创建商品（记录返回的 data.id，回填到 @productId）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "演示商品-流程测试",
  "description": "用于 demo_flow 正常链路",
  "price_fen": 1999
}

### 2. 商品上架
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products/{{productId}}/on-sale
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. 查询商品详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products/{{productId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

## 三、库存模块正常流程
### 4. 初始化库存
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/inventory/init
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product_id": {{productId}},
  "stock_quantity": 100
}

### 5. 增加库存
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/inventory/add
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product_id": {{productId}},
  "quantity": 20
}

### 6. 查询库存
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/inventory/products/{{productId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

## 四、订单模块正常流程
### 7. 创建订单（记录返回的 data.id，回填到 @orderId）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idempotency_key": "demo-order-{{$guid}}",
  "items": [
    {
      "product_id": {{productId}},
      "quantity": 999
    }
  ]
}

### 8. 支付订单
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders/{{orderId}}/pay
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. 完成订单
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders/{{orderId}}/finish
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. 查询订单详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders/{{orderId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
